headline: Oceania Cruises® Celebrates Record-Breaking Launch Day for Brand New Ship
summary: Oceania Cruises®, the world's leading culinary- and destination-focused luxury cruise line, achieved record-breaking booking levels on January 28, 2026, the opening day of reservations for its newest ship, Oceania Sonata. This surpassed the launch-day bookings of Oceania Cruises' previous new ship, Oceania Allura™, by an impressive 45%.

headline: RCL Best Booking Streak Ever: Signal of Strong Cruise Demand in 2026?
summary: Royal Caribbean logs its best seven booking weeks ever, with two-thirds of 2026 capacity booked at record prices, signaling durable cruise demand.

headline: 3 Value Stocks We Keep Off Our Radar
summary: Value investing has produced some of the world’s most famous investing billionaires, including Warren Buffett, David Einhorn, and Seth Klarman, who built their fortunes by purchasing wonderful businesses at reasonable prices. But these hidden gems are few and far between - many stocks that appear cheap often stay that way because they face structural issues.
